2.1 APL Scripting
=================

* Menu:

* Subsection 2.1.1::  Redirect the script file to the stdin of the GNU APL interpreter
* Subsection 2.1.2::  Make the script file executable
* Subsection 2.1.3::  How command line arguments are handled
* Subsection 2.1.4::  Helpful Features for Scripting
